description: Award winning authentic Mexican food... Best taco truck in Texas!!! We have won the prestigious San Antonio readers choice awards since 2011 including the only entry to win both the peoples choice award and the gold medal in the same year!!! We have been in business 6 years... One of the first food trucks in San Antonio.. Our recipes are from all over Mexico... Not tex-mex like most Mexican food here!!! We guarantee you will love it!!
name: Chelas Tacos
